        %% --- Connections & Flow ---
        Principle1 -- Implemented by --> StandardUser
        Principle2 -- Implemented by --> SSD
        
        StandardUser -- Runs --> VMware
        
        VMware -- "Stores VM Files (.vmdk)" --> SSD
    end